To build, go into the src directory and type:

  make

It will generate an executable in the preceding directory called
omgwtfadd. To play, type:

 ./omgwtfadd

You will need SDL and GL packages along with GLUT. A list:

 libGL
 libSDL
 libSDL_net
 libSDL_mixer
 libSDL_image
 libglut

Just be sure to install the development packages for these
libraries.
